Dataset_field.sql_query: select user_id from tbl_users where user_login = '{UserContext.sid}'
select group_name from tbl_groups where group_id = (select group_id from tbl_groupmembers where user_id = '{UserContext.userid}')
select group_concat(queue_id) from tbl_queue_members where object_id = '{UserContext.userid}' and object_type = 0
SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(REPLACE(queue_name,'SP_','')) FROM tbl_queues WHERE queue_name like 'SP_%' AND FIND_IN_SET (queue_id, '{UserContext.userQueues}') <> 0

SELECT CONCAT('', '', GROUP_CONCAT(orderedTable.results SEPARATOR ''), '
Package AMCN ID (PR.ID)TitleSource Asset IDPlatformPress SheetMedia StatusArtwork StatusDelivery Date
') FROM ( SELECT CONCAT( '',IFNULL(mainTable.AMCNID,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.Title,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.sourceID,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.DeliveryPlatform,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.PressSheetStatus,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.mediaStatus,''),'', '',IFNULL(mainTable.artStatus,''),'', '',IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(mainTable.DeliveryDateCalc, '%m/%d/%y'),''),'' ) results FROM ( ( SELECT [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] AMCNID, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Title] Title, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.DeliveryPlatform] DeliveryPlatform, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.DeliveryDate] DeliveryDate, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.ArtworkOffset] ArtworkDueDate, [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.PORTAL_SendDate] DeliveryDateCalc, placement.source sourceID, IF( touch.mediaStatus IS NULL, IF( placement.amcnid IS NULL, 'Not Requested', IF( placement.sourceStatus='Ready for Distribution', 'In Progress', 'Requested' ) ), touch.mediaStatus ) mediaStatus, IF( COUNT([ADAM_Record_Component.ComponentType])=0, 'Not Requested', IF( COUNT([ADAM_Record_Component.ComponentType]) = SUM(IF([ADAM_Record_Component.FileStatus] = 'Ready for Distribution',1,0)), 'Ready for Distribution', IF( SUM(IF([ADAM_Record_Component.PortalRecordStatus] IS NOT NULL,1,0)) = 0, 'Requested', 'In Progress' ) ) ) artStatus, IF( vam.obj IS NULL, 'Not Created', IF( GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT IF([ADAM_NL_Component.FileStatus]='','X',[ADAM_NL_Component.FileStatus]) SEPARATOR '')='Ready for Distribution', 'Ready for Distribution', 'In Progress' ) ) metaStatus, IF( [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Inactive]='true', 'Cancelled', IF( IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Revoked],'') = 'Revoked', [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Revoked], IF( IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered],'') IN ('Accepted','Rejected'), [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered], IF( IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered],'') = 'Delivered', [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.Delivered], IF( IFNULL(a.description,'')='', IF( LOWER([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.PlacementSEND]) = 'new', IFNULL(NULLIF([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.ValidityStatus],''),'New'), IFNULL(vam.PlacementSEND,IFNULL([ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.PlacementSEND],'')) ), IF( -- Awaiting Ack Metadata delivered to Vampire a.def_id = 94439, 'Metadata Sent to Vampire', IF( -- Awaiting Vampire Completion a.def_id = 95362, 'Metadata Received by Vampire', IF( -- Awaiting Ack Legacy Update a.def_id = 105654, 'Update IDs', a.description ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) Status, CASE WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'No Press Sheet' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'No Press Sheet' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] = 'No Press Sheet' THEN 'No Press Sheets' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] like 'Migrated%' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] like 'Migrated%' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] like 'Migrated%' THEN 'Migrated - Needs Checking' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'New' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'New' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] like 'New' THEN 'New' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'In Progress' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'In Progress' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] = 'In Progress' THEN 'In Progress' WHEN [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeriesPressSheetStatus] = 'Press Ready' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.SeasonPressSheetStatus] = 'Press Ready' AND [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery_TMP.EpisodePressSheetStatus] = 'Press Ready' THEN 'Press Ready' ELSE 'In Progress' END AS PressSheetStatus FROM [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery] -- Join to Deliveries to get only the latest instance INNER JOIN ( SELECT MIN(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery] GROUP BY [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] ) maxID ON maxID.obj = [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery].object_id -- JOIN to components (of delivery) for artwork status LEFT JOIN [ADAM_Record_Component] ON [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery].object_id = [ADAM_Record_Component].object_id AND [ADAM_Record_Component.ComponentType] = 'Artwork' -- Join to Vampire version of Deliveries to get the current state in Vampire flow LEFT JOIN ( SELECT object_id obj, [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] amcnid, [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.PORTAL_SendDate] senddate, [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.PlacementSEND] PlacementSEND FROM [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery] -- INNER JOIN (SELECT MAX(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery] -- GROUP BY [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID])maxID ON maxID.obj = [ADAM_NL_PlacementDelivery].object_id ) vam ON vam.amcnid = [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.AMCNID] -- Join to activities to get current state of Vampire flow LEFT JOIN tbl_bpm_activities a ON a.process_id = vam.obj AND a.status = 'active' -- Join to placements table to get the state of the placement LEFT JOIN ( SELECT object_id obj, [ADAM_Record_Placement.AMCNID] amcnid, [ADAM_Record_Placement.HierarchyParentID] hpid, [ADAM_Record_Placement.SourceID] source, [ADAM_Record_Placement.SourceMediaAssetStatus] sourceStatus FROM [ADAM_Record_Placement] INNER JOIN ( SELECT MAX(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_Record_Placement] GROUP BY [ADAM_Record_Placement.AMCNID] ) maxPub ON maxPub.obj = object_id ) placement ON placement.amcnid = [ADAM_Record_PlacementDelivery.HierarchyParentID] -- Join to touchpoints placement table to get the state of the placement LEFT JOIN ( SELECT [ADAM_Touchpoint_Component.HierarchyParentID] amcnid, [ADAM_Touchpoint_Component.FileStatus] mediaStatus FROM [ADAM_Touchpoint_Component] INNER JOIN ( SELECT MAX(object_id) obj FROM [ADAM_Touchpoint_Placement] GROUP BY [ADAM_Touchpoint_Placement.AMCNID] AnnounceDate , [AVAILS_Episode.ReleaseYear] ReleaseYear , '' ReleaseHistoryOriginal , '' ReleaseHistoryPhysicalHV , '' ExceptionFlag , '' RatingSystem , '' RatingValue , '' RatingReason , '' [AVAILS_Transmission] ON ( [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] and [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id={PROCESS::ID} ) LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode_Titles] ON results.DisplayName, results.AssetLanguage, results.Territory, results.WorkType, results.EntryType, results.TitleInternalAlias, results.TitleDisplayUnlimited, results.LocalizationType, results.CompanyDisplayCredit, results.LicenseType, results.LicenseRightsDescription, format.FormatProfile, results.HDR, results.WCG, results.HFR, results.NGAudio, results.StartDateTimeFrom, results.StartDateTimeTo, results.PriceType, results.PriceValue, results.PriceCurrency, results.SRP, results.Description, results.OtherTerms, results.OtherInstructions, results.TitleID , results.EditID, results.AltID, results.ContentID, results.AvailID, results.UV_ID, results.DMA_ID, results.ReportingID, results.Metadata, results.ALID, results.SuppressionLiftDate, results.SpecialPreOrderFulfillDate, results.AnnounceDate, results.ReleaseYear, results.ReleaseHistoryOriginal, results.ReleaseHistoryPhysicalHV, results.ExceptionFlag, results.RatingSystem, results.RatingValue, results.RatingReason, results.RentalDuration, results.WatchDuration, results.CaptionIncluded, results.CaptionExemption, results.Any, results.ContractID, results.ServiceProvider FROM
(SELECT 1 joinval, 'HD' FormatProfile from DUAL UNION SELECT 1 joinval, 'SD' FormatProfile from dual)format
JOIN
(select 1 joinval, [AVAILS_Episode.displayName] DisplayName, 'EN' AssetLanguage, 'US' Territory, 'Movie' WorkType, 'Full Extract' EntryType, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.AlternativeTitles] TitleInternalAlias, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.AlternativeTitles] TitleDisplayUnlimited, '' LocalizationType, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.OwnerNetwork] = 'WE' THEN 'WE tv' ELSE [AVAILS_Episode.OwnerNetwork] END CompanyDisplayCredit, CASE WHEN (([AVAILS_Transmission.Channel] in ('Amazon EST', 'Comcast EST', 'Frontier EST', 'Google Play', 'iTunes Canada TV', 'iTunes USA TV', 'Lionsgate (LGE)', 'Microsoft XBOX', 'Verizon EST', 'Vudu', 'FandangoNOW EST') )) THEN 'EST' WHEN (([AVAILS_Transmission.Channel] in ('AMC+ On Demand', 'WETV+ On Demand', 'ALLBLK', 'AMC+ Canada On Demand') )) THEN 'SVOD' ELSE '' END LicenseType, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Transmission.Prototype] = 'EST - Comcast' THEN 'Library' WHEN ((([AVAILS_Transmission.Prototype] = 'EST - Next Day') OR ([AVAILS_Transmission.Prototype] = 'EST - Store Front Opening (Short Form)')) AND ( [AVAILS_Episode.Platform]= 'Amazon EST')) THEN 'DAB' WHEN ((([AVAILS_Transmission.Prototype] = 'EST - Next Day') OR ([AVAILS_Transmission.Prototype] = 'EST - Store Front Opening (Short Form)')) AND ( [AVAILS_Episode.Platform] <> 'Amazon EST')) THEN 'Next Day TV' ELSE '' END LicenseRightsDescription, '' FormatProfile, '' HDR, '' WCG, '' HFR, '' NGAudio, [AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] StartDateTimeFrom, 'Open' StartDateTimeTo, '' PriceType, '' PriceValue, '' PriceCurrency, '' SRP, '' Description, '' OtherTerms, '' OtherInstructions, '' TitleID , '' EditID, [AVAILS_Episode.exportAMCNID] AltID, [AVAILS_Episode.exportAMCNID] ContentID, '' AvailID, '' UV_ID, '' DMA_ID, '' ReportingID, '' Metadata, [AVAILS_Episode.exportAMCNID] ALID, '' SuppressionLiftDate, '' SpecialPreOrderFulfillDate, '' AnnounceDate, [AVAILS_Episode.ReleaseYear] ReleaseYear, '' ReleaseHistoryOriginal, '' ReleaseHistoryPhysicalHV, '' ExceptionFlag, '' RatingSystem, '' RatingValue, '' RatingReason, '' RentalDuration, '' WatchDuration, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.ClosedCaptionsYN] = 'true' THEN 'Yes' WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.ClosedCaptionsYN] = 'false' THEN 'No' else '' END CaptionIncluded, '' CaptionExemption, '' Any, '' ContractID, [AVAILS_Episode.ServiceProvider] ServiceProvider from [AVAILS_Episode] LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON ( [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] and [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id={PROCESS::ID} ) LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode_Titles] ON ([AVAILS_Episode_Titles].object_id={PROCESS::ID} and [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode_Titles.AMCNID]) LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM] ON ( [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM.HierarchyParentID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] and [AVAILS_ProgramMetadataMRM].object_id={PROCESS::ID} ) where ([AVAILS_Episode].object_id={PROCESS::ID} and [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType]='Movie') group by [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID])results ON results.joinval = format.joinval

SELECT IFNULL([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles.Title],'') AS Title, IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(CAST([AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] AS DATE),'%Y-%d-%m'),'') as LaunchDate, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE [AVAILS_Episode.EpisodeNumber] END AS EpisodeNumber, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE TRIM(LEADING '0' from IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.SeasonNumber],'')) END AS SeasonNumber, IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.corePlatform],[AVAILS_Episode.Platform]) as corePlatform, IFNULL([AVAILS_Transmission.TransmissionTerritory],'') as territory FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id=[AVAILS_Episode].object_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
LEFT JOIN [EST_EXport_data_tmp] ON [EST_EXport_data_tmp].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] IN ('Episode','Program') AND [EST_EXport_data_tmp.exportType] IN ('iTunes Export','SVOD Export') GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission].id

SELECT IFNULL([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles.Title],'') AS Title, IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(CAST([AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] AS DATE),'%Y-%d-%m'),'') as LaunchDate, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE IFNULL(NULLIF([AVAILS_Episode.EpisodeNumber] ,''),'') END AS EpisodeNumber, CASE WHEN [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Short Film') THEN 'NA' ELSE TRIM(LEADING '0' from IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.SeasonNumber],'')) END AS SeasonNumber, IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.corePlatform],[AVAILS_Episode.Platform]) as corePlatform, IFNULL([AVAILS_Transmission.TransmissionTerritory],'') as territory FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id=[AVAILS_Episode].object_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
LEFT JOIN [EST_EXport_data_tmp] ON [EST_EXport_data_tmp].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film') AND [EST_EXport_data_tmp.exportType] IN ('PDS Film Ingest','Vampire Film Ingest') GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission].id
UNION
SELECT IFNULL([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles.Title],'') AS Title, IFNULL(DATE_FORMAT(CAST([AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeFrom] AS DATE),'%Y-%d-%m'),'') as LaunchDate, [AVAILS_Episode.EpisodeNumber] AS EpisodeNumber, TRIM(LEADING '0' from IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.SeasonNumber],'')) AS SeasonNumber, IFNULL([AVAILS_Episode.corePlatform],[AVAILS_Episode.Platform]) as corePlatform, IFNULL([AVAILS_Transmission.TransmissionTerritory],'') as territory FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Titles].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Episode] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Episode.AMCNID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id=[AVAILS_Episode].object_id
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] = [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
LEFT JOIN [EST_EXport_data_tmp] ON [EST_EXport_data_tmp].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_Episode.ShowType] IN ('Series','Interstitial','Special','Pilot','Digital Series') AND [EST_EXport_data_tmp.exportType] IN ('PDS Series Ingest','Vampire Series Ingest') GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission].id

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1"?><Params><sql value="UPDATE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata] LEFT JOIN ( SELECT [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id as parent_ref_id, GROUP_CONCAT([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember_DisplayNames.DisplayName] SEPARATOR ', ') AS DisplayNames FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember.Type] = 'Talent/Actor'
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember_DisplayNames] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember].child_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember_DisplayNames].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Cast_CastMember_DisplayNames].object_id = {PROCESS::ID}
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film')
GROUP BY [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id ) AS GROUPED_NAMES ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = GROUPED_NAMES.parent_ref_id
SET [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.Episodeactors] = GROUPED_NAMES.DisplayNames
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film')

UPDATE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN ( SELECT [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id as parent_ref_id, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Rating] as rating, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Descriptor] as descriptor, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Reason] as reason, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Content] as content, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.UserCode] as usercode FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
INNER JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id AND [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID]
INNER JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem] ON [AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id
INNER JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings].object_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film') AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.Type]=[AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem.Rating_Type] AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_Ratings.UserCode]=[AVAILS_Transmission_PublicationSystem.Rating_UserCode]
GROUP BY [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id ) AS GROUP_RATINGS ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = GROUP_RATINGS.parent_ref_id SET [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.EpisodeTVRating] = GROUP_RATINGS.rating, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.RatingDescriptorTV] = GROUP_RATINGS.descriptor, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.RatingReason] = GROUP_RATINGS.reason, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.RatingUserCode] = GROUP_RATINGS.usercode
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film')
NEW_SQL
UPDATE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata]
LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_VODTitle] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_VODTitle].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_VODTitle].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_VODTitle.VODTitleType] = 'Cutdown'
SET [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.FolderName] = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_VODTitle.content]
WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film')

UPDATE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata] LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] LIKE 'Amazon-Primary%' SET [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.StudioGenreAmazonOnly] = CASE WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] = 'Amazon-Primary-Drama - Crime' THEN 'AMC Plus Drama' WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] = 'Amazon-Primary-Drama - Supernatural' THEN 'AMC Plus Supernatural' WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] = 'Amazon-Primary-Nonfiction - Crime' THEN 'AMC Plus Crime' WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] = 'Amazon-Primary-Nonfiction - Documentary' THEN 'AMC Plus Documentaries' WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] = 'Amazon-Primary-Independent' THEN 'AMC Plus Independent' WHEN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] = 'Amazon-Primary-Horror' THEN 'AMC Plus Horror' ELSE '' END, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AmazonGenre] = ( SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(REPLACE([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre],'Amazon-','') ORDER BY [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] SEPARATOR ', ') from [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup] WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} and [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] like 'Amazon-%' and [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] not like 'Amazon-Primary-%' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film') AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].parent_ref_id ) WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film')

UPDATE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata] LEFT JOIN [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup] ON [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].parent_ref_id AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} SET [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AppleGenre] = ( SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(REPLACE([AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre],'Apple-','') ORDER BY [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] SEPARATOR ', ') from [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup] WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} and [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] like 'Apple-%' and [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup.Genre] not like 'Apple-Primary-%' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] IN ('Movie') AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata_PlatformGenres_GenreGroup].parent_ref_id ) WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] = 'Program' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Movie','Special','Pilot','Short Film')

LEFT JOIN (SELECT [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.Notes] Notes, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id obj, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.AMCNID] AMCNID, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.HierarchyParentID] HierarchyParentID, [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].parent_ref_id parent_ref_id FROM [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata] WHERE [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata].object_id={PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.Notes] > '' AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.TitleType] in ('Episode') AND [AVAILS_ProgramMetadata.ShowType] in ('Series') ) Episode_Notes ON Episode_Notes.obj=[AVAILS_Transmission].object_id AND Episode_Notes.AMCNID = [AVAILS_Transmission.HierarchyParentID] WHERE [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id={PROCESS::ID}
GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission.AMCNID] ) AS summaryNotesTbl ON summaryNotesTbl.AMCNID = [AVAILS_Transmission.AMCNID] SET [AVAILS_Transmission.SummaryNotes] = summaryNotesTbl.Notes WHERE [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id = {PROCESS::ID}

		handle_err_result("ERROR_GET_DATA_RECORD_RETRIEVAL",$result);

#Use for build the string of parameters, depending of value
sub createParamStr{
	my $tempParamStr = $_[0];
	my $tempValue = $_[1];
	my $tempParamName = $_[2];
	my $tempSeparatorSym = $_[3];
	
	if ($tempValue ne "") {
		return $tempParamStr = $tempParamStr . $tempParamName . "=" . $tempValue . $tempSeparatorSym;
	}else {
		return $tempParamStr;
	}
}

sub handle_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
		
    print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Request ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Request ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ? 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body]);

}

sub handle_err_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
	print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Error ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Error ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpCode] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpCode'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpMessage] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpMessage'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.moreInformation] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/moreInformation') 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body]);
}

sub welcomeBannerLog{
	my $dt   = DateTime->now;   # Stores current date and time as datetime object
	my $date = $dt->ymd;   # Retrieves date as a string in 'yyyy-mm-dd' format
	my $time = $dt->hms;   # Retrieves time as a string in 'hh:mm:ss' format

	my $dateProcess = "$date $time";   # creates 'yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss' string
	my $banner = "\n
--------------------------------------------------------

--------------------------------------------------------
	";
	print DEBUGFILE $banner;
}

	my $dt   = DateTime->now;   # Stores current date and time as datetime object
	my $date = $dt->ymd;   # Retrieves date as a string in 'yyyy-mm-dd' format
	my $time = $dt->hms;   # Retrieves time as a string in 'hh:mm:ss' format

	my $banner = "\n
--------------------------------------------------------
  *** End Process **
  DateTime   [" . $dateProcess . "]\n
--------------------------------------------------------
	";
	print DEBUGFILE $banner;
}

#Use for build the string of parameters, depending of value
sub createParamStr{
	my $tempParamStr = $_[0];
	my $tempValue = $_[1];
	my $tempParamName = $_[2];
	my $tempSeparatorSym = $_[3];
	
	if ($tempValue ne "") {
		return $tempParamStr = $tempParamStr . $tempParamName . "=" . $tempValue . $tempSeparatorSym;
	}else {
		return $tempParamStr;
	}
}

sub handle_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
		
    print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Request ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Request ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ? 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body]);

}

sub handle_err_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
	print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Error ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Error ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpCode] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpCode'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpMessage] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpMessage'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.moreInformation] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/moreInformation') 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body]);
}

#Use for build the string of parameters, depending of value
sub createParamStr{
	my $tempParamStr = $_[0];
	my $tempValue = $_[1];
	my $tempParamName = $_[2];
	my $tempSeparatorSym = $_[3];
	
	if ($tempValue ne "") {
		return $tempParamStr = $tempParamStr . $tempParamName . "=" . $tempValue . $tempSeparatorSym;
	}else {
		return $tempParamStr;
	}
}

sub handle_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
		
    print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Request ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	#print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Request ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ? 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body]);

}

sub handle_err_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
	print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Error ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Error ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpCode] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpCode'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpMessage] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpMessage'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.moreInformation] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/moreInformation') 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body]);
}

#Use for build the string of parameters, depending of value
sub createParamStr{
	my $tempParamStr = $_[0];
	my $tempValue = $_[1];
	my $tempParamName = $_[2];
	my $tempSeparatorSym = $_[3];
	
	if ($tempValue ne "") {
		return $tempParamStr = $tempParamStr . $tempParamName . "=" . $tempValue . $tempSeparatorSym;
	}else {
		return $tempParamStr;
	}
}

sub handle_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
		
    print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Request ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	#print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Request ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ? 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body]);

}

sub handle_err_result{

    my $status_code = $_[0];
    my $response_body = $_[1];
	print DEBUGFILE "\nHandle Error ... Init\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Status [". $status_code . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Response [". $response_body . "]\n";
	print DEBUGFILE "Handle Error ... End\n ";
	
	my $sql = 
	"UPDATE [AVAILS_Response] SET 
	[AVAILS_Response.statusCode] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.result] = ?, 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpCode] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpCode'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.httpMessage] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/httpMessage'), 
	[AVAILS_Response.moreInformation] = EXTRACTVALUE(?,'/*/moreInformation') 
	WHERE object_id = {PROCESS::ID}";
	my $db = SYMBOX::DB::Sql($sql,[$status_code,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body,$response_body]);
}

UPDATE [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod] JOIN (SELECT [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].id idVal, [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id objID, IFNULL(MIN(tbl1.sDate),LEFT([AVAILS_Transmission.StartDateTimeTo],10)) endDate FROM [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod] LEFT JOIN (SELECT [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].parent_ref_id parent, [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id obj, [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].id rowID, [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod.StartDate] sDate FROM [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod] WHERE [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod.Authenticated] = 'true')tbl1 ON tbl1.obj = [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id AND tbl1.sDate > [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod.StartDate] AND tbl1.parent = [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].parent_ref_id JOIN [AVAILS_Transmission] ON [AVAILS_Transmission].object_id = [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id AND [AVAILS_Transmission].parent_ref_id = [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].parent_ref_id WHERE [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id = {PROCESS::ID} AND [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod.Unauthenticated] = 'true' GROUP BY [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].id)tbl2 ON tbl2.idVal = [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].id AND tbl2.objID = [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id SET [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod.EndDate] = tbl2.endDate WHERE [AVAILS_Transmission_AttributePeriods_AttributePeriod].object_id = {PROCESS::ID}
